rc=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/32/179c85c463eca7af8fda0bd28e16nts5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F32%2F179c85c463eca7af8fda0bd28e16nts5.JPG&h=2fa56689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《天外世界》是款第一人稱科幻角色扮演遊戲，故事背景設定在銀河系邊緣的太空殖民地，故事敘述主角因為太空船的錯誤而漂流到銀河系邊緣，從冷凍睡眠中醒來後孤身一人的他，將展開闖蕩邊陲殖民地的冒險。遊戲中玩家將打造自己專屬的分身，探索神祕星球環境、依照自己的喜好建立起屬於自己的故事路線。<br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=6f041f42\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=d93d65ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326a271a53b41d9bdf9a63521915afd87587cb3f","tid":1688430,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e310c3f4421d3c35c47e7662cf530b224b0b918e","tid":1688430,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6642888a4d26cba6e8d2e1015f19a65dd03fe0c","tid":1688430,"uid":291